<div class="container">
  <header>
    <img src="/images/logo_white.svg" alt="logo" id="logo">
    <h2 class="hidden">Nav Header</h2>
    <nav id="main-nav">
      <h2 class="hidden">Main Navigation</h2>
      <div id="menuToggle">
        <input type="checkbox" /> <span class="hamburger line1"></span>
        <span class="hamburger line2"></span>
        <ul id="menu">
          <li>
            <a id="about" class="nav-btn" href="#about-us">About Me</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a id="team" class="nav-btn" href="#meet-team">Portfolio</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a id="contact" class="nav-btn" href="#">Contact</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="header-text">
      <p>I am Brazilian and I came to Canada in 2018. 
        I also hold a B.A. in Social Communication, Journalism and an MBA in Corporate Communication. 
        For years, I worked as a reporter, producing and conducting interviews for television programs, 
        newspapers, as well as content for corporate television.</p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section id="about-me">
    <h3>Once upon a time...</h3>
    <div class="about-me-text">
      <p>... a Professional Journalist with a lot of experience in the advertising industry, 
        agency interface, customer services and client relationship in Brazil, decides to 
        improve her knowledge in every aspect of Digital Communication through a Diploma Program 
        at Fanshawe College in Canada. That's me! and by doing so I will be able to apply all the knowledge 
        aquired at this program and before into a new career opportunity. 
        It wasn’t easy, but I am a dedicated and persistent professional who strives to excel 
        in each and every project I work in.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="icons">
      <i class="fas fa-globe-americas fa-7x"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-microphone fa-7x"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-newspaper fa-7x"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-tv fa-7x"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-user-graduate fa-7x"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-wine-glass-alt fa-7x"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="quote">
      <p class="quote-text">
      <span class="quotes">&ldquo;</span>
        Renata is an incredible professional. Her enthusiasm and dedication accompanies her 
        in everything she intends to do. She has a strategy vision, planning capacity and 
        Portuguese spotless writing. She is an excellent leader, motivating and always willing 
        to help. I learned a lot during the time we worked together, mainly because she is 
        flexible to solve problems and persistent to obtain the best results.
      <span class="quotes">&rdquo;</span>
      <span class="author">Bruna Scoralick Queiroz - Marketing Strategy Specialist</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="portfolio">
    <div class="portfolio-header">
      <h3>Portfolio</h3>
      <div class="portfolio-header-txt">
        <p>My job requires constant attention to deadlines and quality control of production. 
          During my education in Interactive Media Design, I worked on many awesome assignments, 
          I chose some of them to share below.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="projects">
      {{#each projects}}
      <div class="project">
        <h2 class="title">{{ proj_title }}</h2>
        <a href="">
          <img src="/images/{{ proj_img_sm }}" alt="{{ proj_title }}">
        </a>
        <p>{{ proj_summary }}</p>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
      </div>
      <div class="quote">
        <p class="quote-text">
        <span class="quotes">&ldquo;</span>
          Renata is a dedicated professional and a very creative person. Her ideas bring dynamic to the Elas TV Show! It was a lot of work but, a big project that worked and we are very proud of that.
        <span class="quotes">&rdquo;</span>
        <span class="author">Renata Lima - Communication Consultant</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="contact">
    <h3>Give me a shout <i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i></h3>
      <form>  
      <div class="contentform">
          <div id="sendmessage"> Your message has been sent successfully. Thank you. </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <p>Full Name</p>
            <span class="icon-case"><i class="fa fa-male"></i></span>
                <input type="text" name="nom" id="nom" data-rule="required" data-msg="Vérifiez votre saisie sur les champs : Le champ 'Nom' doit être renseigné."/>
          <div class="validation"></div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <p>E-mail</p>    
            <span class="icon-case"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i></span>
            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" data-rule="email" data-msg="Vérifiez votre saisie sur les champs : Le champ 'E-mail' est obligatoire."/>
            <div class="validation"></div>
          </div>  
          <div class="form-group">
          <p>Subject</p>   
          <span class="icon-case"><i class="fa fa-comment-o"></i></span>
              <input type="text" name="sujet" id="sujet" data-rule="required" data-msg="Vérifiez votre saisie sur les champs : Le champ 'Sujet' doit être renseigné."/>
              <div class="validation"></div>
          </div>
      
          <div class="form-group">
          <p>Message</p>
          <span class="icon-case"><i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i></span>
              <textarea name="message" rows="14" data-rule="required" data-msg="Vérifiez votre saisie sur les champs : Le champ 'Message' doit être renseigné."></textarea>
              <div class="validation"></div>
          </div> 
        </div> 
      </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn-contact">Send</button>   
  </form> 
  </section>
  <section id="video">
    <h3>Demo Reel</h3>
    <div class="quote">
      <video src="/video/cunha_renata_morph_cd4.mp4" type="video/mp4" controls></video>
    </div>
  </section>
  <footer>
    <img src="/images/logo_white.svg" alt="logo" id="logo">
    <p>&copy; Renata Cunha</p>
  </footer>
</div>